            ┌ Help ───────────────────────────────────────────────┐
            │                                                     │
            │  Prefix key: C-g (tmux-style)                       │
            │    Keys always go to the focused pane;              │
            │    press C-g first for app actions:                 │
            │                                                     │
            │    C-g h/j/k/l   Move focus between panes           │
            │    C-g c         New tab                            │
            │    C-g x         Close tab                          │
            │    C-g n/C-g p   Next/Prev tab                      │
            │    C-g 1..9      Jump to tab N                      │
            │    C-g w         Fuzzy workspace switcher           │
            │    C-g )/C-g (   Next/Prev workspace                │
            │    C-g `         Previous workspace (toggle)        │
            │    C-g N         New workspace                      │
            │    C-g e         Edit workspace                     │
            │    C-g i         Workspace info                     │
            │    C-g R         Create worktree (GitHub-only)      │
            │    C-g g         Git (lazygit tab)                  │
            │    C-g :         Command palette                    │
            │    C-g /         Fuzzy file search                  │
            │    C-g [         Terminal scroll mode               │
            │    C-g y         AI Chat                            │
            │    C-g D         Dashboard                          │
            │    C-g o         Logs                               │
            │    C-g A         Manage agents                      │
            │    C-g V         Manage providers                   │
            │    C-g a         About                              │
            │    C-g ?         This help                          │
            │    C-g q         Quit                               │
            │    C-g C-g       Send C-g to terminal               │
            │    Esc           Cancel pending prefix              │
            │                                                     │
            │  Terminal scroll mode (C-g [)                       │
            │    k/j           Scroll up/down                     │
            │    ctrl-u/ctrl-d Page up/down                       │
            │    g/G           Top/Bottom                         │
            │    /             Search                             │
            │    q/esc         Exit scroll mode                   │
